Araw-araw ba siyang nagtatrabaho?

258
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:28,560
Halos araw-araw.

259
00:19:28,560 --> 00:19:31,200
Pagkatapos ng klase, pumunta siya
sa convenience store,

260
00:19:31,200 --> 00:19:32,770
tapos pumupunta rito para sa closing shift.

261
00:19:32,770 --> 00:19:34,170
Nakakapagod talaga.

262
00:19:35,240 --> 00:19:36,230
Kung

263
00:19:36,340 --> 00:19:39,640
may makakapag-alaga lang sa
aming maliit na part-timer na si Junjia,

264
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:41,970
malamang hindi na niya kailangang magtrabaho nang ganito kahirap.

265
00:19:46,120 --> 00:19:46,850
Oo.

266
00:19:46,850 --> 00:19:47,950
Oo.

267
00:19:48,180 --> 00:19:48,580
Oo.

268
00:19:49,820 --> 00:19:51,190
Siya at ang kanyang tiyahin

269
00:19:51,190 --> 00:19:53,050
ay umaasa sa isa't isa,
namumuhay nang matipid.

270
00:19:53,050 --> 00:19:54,690
Dati-rati'y walang laman ang kanyang refrigerator.

271
00:19:54,690 --> 00:19:55,910
-Halos wala siyang makain.
-Walang laman!

272
00:19:55,910 --> 00:19:57,120
Kalaunan, kumain pa siya

273
00:19:57,120 --> 00:19:58,040
mga nag-expire na almusal.

274
00:19:58,040 --> 00:19:58,990
Mga nag-expire na almusal!

275
00:19:58,990 --> 00:20:01,160
Kawawa naman.

276
00:20:01,430 --> 00:20:02,130
Seryoso.

277
00:20:03,060 --> 00:20:03,960
Siya ba ay

278
00:20:04,960 --> 00:20:06,620
lagi na lang ganito ang buhay?

279
00:20:08,300 --> 00:20:10,140
Kaya sana'y alagaan mong mabuti

280
00:20:10,140 --> 00:20:11,780
ang aming part-timer at inaalagaan siya.

281
00:20:11,780 --> 00:20:12,310
Okay?

282
00:20:13,500 --> 00:20:14,260
Okay?

283
00:20:17,910 --> 00:20:18,850
Kaya ko ba?

284
00:20:31,060 --> 00:20:32,230
Siya,

285
00:20:34,550 --> 00:20:36,950
Nilinis ko ang lunchbox.

286
00:20:38,840 --> 00:20:39,810
At ito.

287
00:20:43,810 --> 00:20:44,820
Isang kwelyo ng pusa?

288
00:20:45,650 --> 00:20:47,150
Paano mo nalaman na may pusa ako?

289
00:20:47,540 --> 00:20:49,710
Madalas kong napapansin ang balahibo ng pusa sa iyo.

290
00:20:50,360 --> 00:20:51,460
Gayundin,

291
00:20:51,710 --> 00:20:53,080
noong huling beses na nawalan ka ng malay,

292
00:20:53,250 --> 00:20:54,650
Tinulungan ko na buhatin ang bag mo

293
00:20:55,350 --> 00:20:57,810
at aksidenteng nakita ang wallpaper ng telepono mo.

294
00:20:59,140 --> 00:21:00,000
Hindi ko kaya.

295
00:21:00,520 --> 00:21:01,320
