296
00:21:02,090 --> 00:21:03,290
Hindi ka ba nagtatrabaho?

297
00:21:03,830 --> 00:21:06,160
Hindi mo naman talaga kailangang gastusin ang perang iyan.

298
00:21:06,730 --> 00:21:07,690
Ayos lang.

299
00:21:07,690 --> 00:21:10,060
Nag-iipon naman ako mula sa part-time job ko.

300
00:21:13,870 --> 00:21:15,240
