313
00:21:40,660 --> 00:21:42,200
at pinaalalahanan akong kumain.

314
00:21:43,100 --> 00:21:44,410
Noong ako'y nasaktan,

315
00:21:44,560 --> 00:21:46,220
Tinulungan mo pa akong bendahan.

316
00:21:46,900 --> 00:21:48,570
Sa tingin ko dapat akong gumawa ng paraan.

317
00:21:53,040 --> 00:21:53,910
Pasensya na

318
00:21:54,910 --> 00:21:56,180
